      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just doesn't feel like \"random environmental stimuli.\" if that were the case, i'd be dreaming about like, a hundred different things. but it's always this one specific brand. and i'm starting to wonder if there's a reason they'd go through all that trouble just for one energy drink. like, what if they aren't just trying to sell me a drink, but they're testing how well these subconscious signals actually work? if they can get a brand into my head while i'm unconscious, what else could they be doing?",
